[## [SECTION: Common Errors and Fixes — Phases 9 & 10]]


110
04:03:00,000 --> 04:03:06,000
Let me walk through common errors in Phases 9 and 10.
And how to fix them.

111
04:03:06,000 --> 04:03:12,000
Error one. cilium connectivity test fails.
The cause is kube-proxy still running.

112
04:03:12,000 --> 04:03:18,000
The fix is to delete the kube-proxy DaemonSet.
kubectl delete ds kube-proxy in kube-system.

113
04:03:18,000 --> 04:03:24,000
Error two. ArgoCD pods stuck Pending.
Cilium not ready when ArgoCD installs.

114
04:03:24,000 --> 04:03:30,000
Apply default-deny-all.yaml after ArgoCD is running.
Not before.

115
04:03:30,000 --> 04:03:36,000
Error three. OutOfSync never resolves.
Ignored differences not set.

116
04:03:36,000 --> 04:03:42,000
Add HPA slash spec slash replicas to ignoreDifferences in ApplicationSet.
This prevents ArgoCD from fighting with the HPA.

117
04:03:42,000 --> 04:03:48,000
Error four. Falco permission denied on eBPF.
EKS managed node missing BPF capability.

118
04:03:48,000 --> 04:03:54,000
Use driver.kind module on older EKS AMIs.
Or upgrade to AL2023 which supports eBPF.

119
04:03:54,000 --> 04:04:00,000
Error five. Rules not loading.
ConfigMap not mounted.

120
04:04:00,000 --> 04:04:06,000
Check extraVolumeMounts path matches rules_file in falco.yaml.
The mount path must be slash etc slash falco slash rules.d.

121
04:04:06,000 --> 04:04:12,000
Error six. Falcosidekick not routing to Slack.
Webhook URL not set.

122
04:04:12,000 --> 04:04:18,000
Use dash set falcosidekick.config.slack.webhookurl equals dollar SLACK_WEBHOOK.
The URL must be valid.

123
04:04:18,000 --> 04:04:24,000
Error seven. L7 policy blocks health check.
Path mismatch.

124
04:04:24,000 --> 04:04:30,000
Verify slash health is in api-l7-policy.yaml ingress rules.
The health endpoint must be explicitly allowed.

125
04:04:30,000 --> 04:04:36,000
Error eight. ArgoCD sync window blocks prod.
Correct behavior.

126
04:04:36,000 --> 04:04:42,000
Use argocd app sync dash dash force only during allowed window.
Otherwise the sync is denied.

127
04:04:42,000 --> 04:04:48,000
Error nine. istioctl shows plaintext traffic.
PeerAuthentication not applied.

128
04:04:48,000 --> 04:04:54,000
Check peer-auth-strict-mtls.yaml is applied in financial-rag namespace.
The policy must be present.

129
04:04:54,000 --> 04:05:00,000
Error ten. Gitleaks false positive.
Test passwords in YAML.

130
04:05:00,000 --> 04:05:06,000
Add pattern to allowlist in dot gitleaks.toml.
The test passwords should be excluded.

131
04:05:06,000 --> 04:05:12,000
Bookmark this section.
When you hit an error, you'll know exactly where to look.


